column16: Kevin Pillar flies out to left fielder Darrell Ceciliani.
Danny Valencia homers (3) on a fly ball to left center field.   Ezequiel Carrera scores.    Russell Martin scores.
Russell Martin singles on a ground ball to center fielder Juan Lagares.   Justin Smoak scores.    Ezequiel Carrera to 3rd.
Ezequiel Carrera singles on a bunt ground ball to first baseman Lucas Duda.   Josh Donaldson scores.    Justin Smoak to 2nd.
Edwin Encarnacion grounds into a force out, third baseman Ruben Tejada to second baseman Dilson Herrera.   Josh Donaldson to 3rd.    Jose Bautista out at 2nd.    Edwin Encarnacion to 1st.
Jose Bautista walks.   Josh Donaldson to 2nd.
